title: The One After Ross Says Rachel
synopsis: Ross and Emily get married, but she cannot forgive him for calling her Rachel during the vows. Chandler and Monica search for a place to have sex.

title: The One with All the Kissing
synopsis: Chandler kisses both Rachel and Phoebe in order to cover up a kiss he gave to Monica. Rachel finally tells Ross her feelings.

title: The One Hundredth
synopsis: Phoebe goes into labor and is stuck with a doctor who is obsessed with the show "Happy Days." Monica plans a date with a male nurse to spite Chandler.

title: The One Where Phoebe Hates PBS
synopsis: The gang discovers that Phoebe hates PBS. Emily tells Ross she'll give him a second chance only if he cuts all ties with Rachel.

title: The One with the Kips
synopsis: Chandler and Monica plan a trip to Atlantic City for some private time. When Joey discovers that they are dating, they swear him to secrecy.

title: The One with the Yeti
synopsis: Monica and Rachel are afraid of a hairy new neighbor -- until they find out how handsome he is with his hair cut.

title: The One Where Ross Moves In
synopsis: After getting kicked out of his apartment, Ross moves in temporarily with Chandler and Joey, driving all three of them crazy.

title: The One with All the Thanksgivings
synopsis: It's Thanksgiving, and the gang remembers former terrible Thanksgiving experiences. Chandler tells Monica that he loves her.

title: The One with Ross's Sandwich
synopsis: Ross becomes upset when someone at work takes his sandwich from the refrigerator and eats it. Joey tries to cover for Chandler and Monica's dating.

title: The One with the Inappropriate Sister
synopsis: Phoebe collects money for the Salvation Army during the holidays. Rachel is disturbed by her date's inappropriate relationship with his sister.

title: The One with All the Resolutions
synopsis: The friends all make New Year's resolutions, but it looks like Rachel's resolution -- to stop gossiping -- is going to be the hardest to keep.

title: The One with Chandler's Work Laugh
synopsis: Ross dates Janice after discovering that Emily is getting remarried. Monica hates the fake laugh that Chandler uses in response to his boss's jokes.

title: The One with Joey's Bag
synopsis: Phoebe meets her father at her grandmother's funeral. Chandler discovers that Monica gives bad massages. Rachel dresses Joey for an audition.

title: The One Where Everybody Finds Out
synopsis: Ross rents an apartment with a window facing Monica and Rachel's place. Phoebe sees Monica and Chandler having sex and learns the truth.

title: The One with the Girl Who Hits Joey
synopsis: Joey's girlfriend likes to punch him. Ross alienates his new neighbors when he refuses to contribute to the retirement donation for the janitor.

title: The One with the Cop
synopsis: After Phoebe finds a police badge, she uses it to do good deeds. Joey worries that he is in love with Monica.

title: The One with Rachel's Inadvertent Kiss
synopsis: Rachel accidentally kisses the man interviewing her for a job. Joey becomes obsessed with a woman living in Ross' apartment complex.

title: The One Where Rachel Smokes
synopsis: Rachel starts smoking when she realizes that her boss and co-workers at her new job are smokers. Joey and Ben audition for a commercial.

title: The One Where Ross Can't Flirt
synopsis: Ross tries to flirt with the pizza delivery girl, with horrible results. Rachel loses a pair of earrings that Monica had lent to Phoebe.

title: The One with the Ride-Along
synopsis: While the men are out, Emily leaves a message for Ross. Rachel, who was in Ross's apartment at the time, hears the message and accidentally erases it.

title: The One with the Ball
synopsis: Gary asks Phoebe to move in with him. Monica and Chandler join Ross and Joey in a game of catch that lasts for hours.

title: The One with Joey's Big Break
synopsis: Joey and Chandler take a road trip to Las Vegas, where Joey has landed the lead role in a movie. But the two argue and Joey goes on alone.

title: The One in Vegas: Part 1
synopsis: The gang decides to go out to Las Vegas to surprise Joey and to celebrate Monica's and Chandler's one-year anniversary.

title: The One in Vegas: Part 2
synopsis: Monica and Chandler reconcile and, on the roll of the dice, decide to go to a chapel and get married immediately.
